reviewText: This is outstanding !! A must for every Petra fan !!
The dvd of this video was edited and cuts most of the Gospel out, also a swell testimony from the keyboardist.

This is a very very good Petra, they were never able to capture the tightness and musicianship after this era again in my eyes.  Greg X. Volz turned down the lead singer position for REO Speedwagon 6 weeks before joining Petra....Also ...you do not have to pay $60 for this video..I got it for $18 on DVD from petramerchandise.com  a nice trip down memory lane.
